{"title":"美国迷","authors":["马凡陀"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":10,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国迷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马凡陀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要不惜牺牲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献身给美国”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——上海女参议员陈某语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头戴美国帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身穿美国衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚登美国鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满口ＡＢＣ。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开口上帝罚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闭口Son of bitch（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜作美国梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来黄脸皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听美国话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心窍美国迷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手开美国枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准亲兄弟…………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：按字直译为“母狗（或狼）的儿子”，发音为“森—阿夫—卑奇”，是美国人骂人的一句口头语，正如中国人说的“狗入的”一样。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}